I know you telephoned because you wanted to say something.

740
01:00:35,330 --> 01:00:37,410
 Exactly.

741
01:00:40,550 --> 01:00:44,920
 You keep asking about this incident.  Why is your thinking so limited?

742
01:00:45,830 --> 01:00:48,050
 Do you think this is the end?

743
01:00:48,860 --> 01:00:51,930
Does that mean the next crime has been planned?

744
01:00:51,930 --> 01:00:53,990
 That's what I am saying.

745
01:00:57,180 --> 01:00:59,590
What's your plan?

746
01:01:01,220 --> 01:01:02,800
 Seo Hyeon Tae.

747
01:01:02,800 --> 01:01:04,870
 What?  Who?

748
01:01:06,890 --> 01:01:09,770
The head of Seoryun Group.

749
01:01:09,770 --> 01:01:12,740
Seo. Hyeon. Tae.

750
01:01:31,450 --> 01:01:33,050
Mom.

751
01:01:33,640 --> 01:01:35,960
Can't you wake up?

752
01:01:38,270 --> 01:01:42,450
You need to eat something so you can have some energy to go to the hospital.

753
01:01:47,420 --> 01:01:49,390
Are you very sick?

754
01:02:01,270 --> 01:02:03,360
You came.

755
01:02:19,340 --> 01:02:21,610
Director Seo.

756
01:02:29,660 --> 01:02:31,180
What?

757
01:02:38,980 --> 01:02:46,020

758
01:03:04,520 --> 01:03:07,660
 Chimera

759
01:03:07,660 --> 01:03:10,500
 It's completely different from Chimera.

760
01:03:10,500 --> 01:03:13,230
 There is something you haven't told me about my father's death, isn't there?

761
01:03:13,230 --> 01:03:18,370
 I'm willing to take dangerous risks but aren't you?

762
01:03:18,370 --> 01:03:19,930
 What's your identity?

763
01:03:19,930 --> 01:03:20,990
 A monster.

764
01:03:20,990 --> 01:03:24,300
 Let's find the blacklist from the Seoryun legal team first.

765
01:03:24,300 --> 01:03:26,060
 If you do something foolish, we will all die together.

766
01:03:26,060 --> 01:03:27,650
 Team Leader, please investigate him.

767
01:03:27,650 --> 01:03:29,690
 It's the investigator's house.  I think he's with her.

768
01:03:29,690 --> 01:03:32,120
 You're not the Chimera. You're a phony.

769
01:03:32,120 --> 01:03:34,650
 What do you know?  What do you know?

770
01:03:34,650 --> 01:03:36,990
 Should I tell you the truth?
